data.description: Positioned in the sought-after locale of Westwood Village, this impeccably presented home offers a blend of style, function, and unparalleled convenience. Boasting a strategic layout encompassing four spacious bedrooms, this property has been meticulously crafted to cater to modern living standards. The kitchen features ample space and a designated dining area, perfect for entertaining or casual meals. The light-filled living area on the upper level effortlessly complements the two well-appointed bedrooms, culminating in a harmonious space that exudes comfort and sophistication. A full bathroom, designed with contemporary finishes, completes this level with elegance. Venture downstairs to discover a versatile family room, primed for relaxation or entertainment. The master bedroom, emphasizing privacy and luxury, is paired with an en-suite bathroom that promises tranquility. Adjacent is a multi-purpose room that can cater to diverse needs, be it a home office, gym, or guest room. Outside, the generous, fully fenced backyard presents an oasis of opportunity, while the property's frontage offers ample off-street parking, ensuring both aesthetics and functionality are addressed. Home is n close proximity to the golf course, reservoir, shopping, and entertainment hubs, this home not only provides an exceptional living environment but also guarantees convenience at your doorstep.Don't miss this exceptional opportunity to Get Your Golden Key!
